Package com.aql.message.mo

Interface Summary
InboundReceiver Provides a contract to receive inbound objects, either StatusUpdates or MOSmsMessage objects.
 

Class Summary
AqlInboundServlet Receives the information in the call back made from Aql concerning the Geo MO message data for virtual mobile numbers.
MOSmsMessage A Mobile Originating, (MO), message sent from a phone to aql.
StatusUpdate The status of an MTSmsMessage which can be one of a number of states
